  <div class="page-tools-panel">
    <div class="panel-citation">
      <strong>Suggested Citation:</strong>"3 Brief History of Supercomputing." National Research Council.  2005. <em>Getting Up to Speed: The Future of Supercomputing</em>. Washington, DC: The National Academies Press. doi: 10.17226/11148.      <div href="#" class="panel-close">&times;</div>
