        </td>
      </tr><tr><td class="listnum">
          <a id="p2000bf3a8960063005"></a>

          <p class="endnotenumtext"><sup>40</sup>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
        </td>

        <td valign="top">
          <p class="footnote">Ibid., p. 108.</p>
        </td>
      </tr><tr><td class="listnum">
          <a id="p2000bf3a8960063006"></a>

          <p class="endnotenumtext"><sup>41</sup>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
        </td>

        <td valign="top">
          <p class="footnote">Office of the Secretary of Defense. 2002. <em>Report on High Performance Computing for the National Security Community</em>.</p>
        </td>
      </tr></table></div>


              </div>
            </div>
